<br>
Winged Courier was exactly that.  A druid or shaman could target another character and transfer an item to them accross great distances.   The problem was targeting them but was basicly a CoH for items.   Original rummors were that the only copies of the spell were found on the roof of the Shaman guild in Halas which required Levetation to get to.   Unfortunately, being a WE Druid from Kelethin by the time I could make it over there, it was removed. <br>
<br>
Mitty in Kerra was a Horrendous camp.  Hours of sitting there doing agro control, killing her and waiting for the next spawn.   I got 20+ kills in on her before they changed the quest then around 80 on the fungus.   Used to get so mad at copper rings.  <br>
<br>
The quest to destroy one of each of 4 rusty swords netted a tarnished scimitar which I used for several levels till I got a combine hammer for 20pp at lv 14 (took me a week to raise that much). <br>
<br>
Shakey needs stuffing and a new head.. I didn't know he could talk..<br>
<br>
Edit: didn't see number 6 till I posted..  Gnasher .. boy ,did that almost 3 years ago.. lets see note to gnasher, kill get head or note... turn in and watch a bartender die.. I think you get a moonstone or booze.. can't remember that far back. sheezzz it is a shame to be a senile druid.  <br>
<br>
But I am too old so can't answer here.  <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ukulothar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kulothar</A> at: 4/13/02 12:48:18 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/udruisilladakilla.showPublicProfile?language=EN>DRUISILLA  DA  KILLA</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(4/29/02 9:58:55 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovefrm29.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=5.topic&index=39>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Trivia Questions for the Youngin's</span><hr size=1> Mitty could actually drop any of the rings the gold being the second most rare for her, and copper the common, the plat one from guy in befallen molter,. 36 straight hours of mitty ( , and now the item really sucks ) keke.<br>
